snippet.title: WorldNeverland - Elnea Kingdom | First 25 Minutes | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
First Look of WorldNeverland - Elnea Kingdom on Nintendo Switch

The kingdom simulation game where you immigrate to an imaginary kingdom and enjoy your free life.
This is the latest game of the World Never Land (Nickname is WorNeva) series. This is the imaginary kingdom that lives in the computer. You can walk wherever you wish to go.

(No Commentary)
